  "content": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 1,
      "text": "Overview"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Below wiki page explains the recovery timer relation with SCU Watch dogs"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "SMU Recovery Timer - XC-CT China - Docupedia (bosch.com)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "This wiki page explains how the timeout value is calculated for recovery timer"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Default value of Recovery timer registers"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Calculation%20of%20SMU%20Recovery%20timer/image-2023-9-4_16-35-46.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Calculation of SMU Recovery timer/image-2023-9-4_16-35-46.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Calculation of recovery timer"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Recovery time duration = RTC.RTD * FSMU_FS tick time"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "FSMU_FS tick time =1/FSMU_FS Clock"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "FSMU_FS Clock= fBACK/FSP.PRE1"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "fBACK=100MHZ ( internal clock )"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Initial clock value after reset"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Calculation%20of%20SMU%20Recovery%20timer/image-2023-9-4_17-0-3.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Calculation of SMU Recovery timer/image-2023-9-4_17-0-3.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Recovery timer value after Reset"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Recovery timer initial duration = (0x3FFF * 2)/100 MHz = 32,766/100 MHz = 0.3 ms"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "Recovery timer configuration for 20ms"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "o get the recovery time as 20ms the value to be configured is:"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "RTC.RTD=Recovery time duration / FSMU_FS tick time"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "=20ms/ (1/(100MHz/2))"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "=20ms * (100MHz/2)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "=0.02 * 50000000"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "=1000000  = F4240"
    }
  ],
